NK075(bu)004:1: // slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i thugs thigs 'di la don gsum ste /
NK075(bu)004:6: rgya gar mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:10: dam bca' bsgrub pa dngos dang /
NK075(bu)004:11: man ngag rgya mtsho brtsam tshul dang /
NK075(bu)004:13: sgo nas bshad par dam bca' ba dang 'brel tshul lo //
NK075(bu)004:18: rang bzhin gyi snang ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:21: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:26: thog mar ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:28: don rtogs par bya ba'i phyir 'khrul dang ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK075(bu)004:29: snang ba dang rgyud kyi nges tshig go //
NK075(bu)004:31: sems 'di skad rigs rgyud med pa la 'khor 'das
NK075(bu)004:32: su snang zhing ngo bo lhun grub tu bstan pa
NK075(bu)004:33: dang / tha dwang rigs dad lhun grub tu gcig
NK075(bu)004:34: pa'i sems nyid mtha' thug med du cir yang snang
NK075(bu)004:36: cir dper na yang snang du rung yang rkyen gyis
NK075(bu)004:37: bsgyur bas snang du btub pa'i dpe don dngos dang
NK075(bu)004:38: / log spyir ni rtog gi snang ba don la rang rgyud du med pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:40: ma nor ba'i mtshan nyid la brgyad de /
NK075(bu)004:41: gnyis sems rgyud su 'dod pa lhun grub la skyon brjod pa nyid 'khrul pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:42: 'khor kun nas 'das tha dad la skyon brjod de tha mi dad du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:43: thams cad log rtog spang du med pa'i dpe'i don dang /
NK075(bu)004:44: blo dngos su 'byed pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)004:45: dag pa sgra ci bzhin du 'dzin pa 'khrul zhing
NK075(bu)004:46: mi 'dzin pa 'khrul zhing mi 'dzin pa mi 'khrul
NK075(bu)004:48: yod las btsal thabs yod med gnyis kar tshol ba 'khrul ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:49: de nas don dbyer med la lhun grub phyogs gcig par 'dzin pa 'khrul pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:50: bden ces gnyis dbyer med yin tshul gyi dpe don
NK075(bu)004:51: bstan cing ci bzhin pa'i don phyogs 'go tsam gyis
NK075(bu)004:55: lung rigs phyin ci kyi sgo nas 'khrul bar snang
NK075(bu)004:56: dus gnas lugs chos nyid las ma g.yos par bstan
NK075(bu)004:57: cing ma rig ye shes tha dad la skyon brjod
NK075(bu)004:58: cing gnyis med du bstan pa'i dpe don dang /
NK075(bu)004:59: rgyud lo dang kyi nges tshig go //
NK075(bu)004:61: snang bden pa ba'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)004:62: de sa ga nyid dang snang ba yin tshul lung gis gsal ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:66: bstan 'khrul gzhi pa dang bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:72: gzhi drug gis sgro skur dang bral bar bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:73: gzhi sgro 'dogs yod pa la 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)004:74: skur pa med pa la 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)004:75: gnyis la la med phyogs gcig pa la 'khrul pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)004:76: thun don nyid mong ma yin pa gnyis med la 'khrul pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:78: ma rig ces pas ngo ma ma shes te 'khrul pa spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:79: bye brag phye ste bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:95: ngo bo rang byung nyid kyi rgyu dang /
NK075(bu)004:97: kun tu rtog lhan cig byed pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:98: de'i rkyen nye bar len pa'i dang /
NK075(bu)004:101: las khams gsum dang nyon mongs rgyud lnga pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:103: de yi de kho na nyid kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK075(bu)004:104: rgyu'o de dang theg pas ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:105: gdul bya'i snang ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:109: gdul bya'i snang ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:110: mchog gi theg pa bkar te bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:112: ngo rang bzhin bo'i nges tshig dang /
NK075(bu)004:113: theg de dang pa'i khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)004:114: gdul phyin ci bya'i snang ba bsam yas pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:115: theg pa mchog la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:116: theg mchog rkyen pa mchog gi rnam grangs bstan pa dang de /
NK075(bu)004:117: gtan la dbab tshul bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:119: lam sgyu 'phrul rkyen yi ge'i rgyud 'di gdul bya'i
NK075(bu)004:120: dbang po rno rtul gyis phye bas gtan dbab tshul
NK075(bu)004:122: yan lag rgyas pa bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:125: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:126: tha ma la 'bras bu lam gyis thob par byed
NK075(bu)004:127: pas lam shes pa'i rgyur 'bru re nas bstan pa'o
NK075(bu)004:130: gdul bya thabs gsum pa lam grol lam du bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:136: rgyud nges pa'i dang ston pa thun mong ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:137: che ba'i de nam mtshan dang don bstan brtag rang gi ngo bo'o mtshan no //
NK075(bu)004:138: 'bring la don dam rnam par dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:139: bstan nyi ma'i pa dang bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:141: shes par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK075(bu)004:142: bar du thun mong dang mchog gis lam nyams su blang ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:143: tha ma drod dang ldan pas 'bras bu mthong la sbyor ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:147: lam dang shes bya 'bras bu'i chos rang gi skabs su 'byung bas 'dir ma bstan pa'i 'thad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:158: thabs snga ma'i lam gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)004:159: shes rab grol lam gyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK075(bu)004:164: khyad bla ma'ang par don gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK075(bu)004:165: thun mong rtags kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK075(bu)004:171: 'gro ba khro bo gang mos su sgom pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:176: sdud pa po thor bu dang /
NK075(bu)004:177: dus sku yi dang bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:181: tshad ces gnyis bstan rkyen gleng bslang ba la gsum ste /
NK075(bu)004:188: dgos tshig don ched kyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:189: bar du thun mong dang mchog gi lam bgrod tshul la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:190: spyir bar du bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:191: mchog gi lam khyad par du bstan pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:200: cig phyi ma char ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:212: cig gcig ni char ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:216: ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:231: ma rtogs bzhi pa pa'i skyon dang /
NK075(bu)004:232: rtogs lnga pa pa'i yan tan no //
NK075(bu)004:237: dpe gling bzhi dang don no //
NK075(bu)004:240: gang gi don du gnyer ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:242: lta rigs med bas gzhan sel lugs dang /
NK075(bu)004:243: sgom bsam gyis pas bsal bya'o //
NK075(bu)004:245: dbang po drug ngo bo dngos dang /
NK075(bu)004:246: mthong de la'ang ba'i khyad par dang /
NK075(bu)004:247: nges gsang ba'i tshig dang zhar la theg pa spyi'i mtshan nyid du 'dod pa nor ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:249: spyi'i de bas mtshan nyid du lta bas gsang sngags
NK075(bu)004:250: mi rtogs pa dang yid rdo rje kyi mi rtog
NK075(bu)004:252: sgra kun tu ci bzhin du rtog cing ldog pa tshol bas lta ba dam pas dbul ba'o //
NK075(bu)004:254: de rjes bstan pa dang bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:256: de 'byung rlung bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK075(bu)004:258: de yi phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:259: phyag gang smin rgya spros pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:260: lnga pa bar chad med pa gnyis dang /
NK075(bu)004:261: rgya mtsho thar lam ting nge 'dzin no /
NK075(bu)004:269: khyad par skyon dang yon de la tan no //
NK075(bu)004:274: gzhan thun mong ma yin pa thabs lam gyi spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:275: grol lam gyi khyad par lam dang sar mthun par spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:277: gcig shos dpe'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:278: don gyi sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:279: snga ma lam rang rang gi spyod pa khyad par gyi spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:280: rgyas par bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK075(bu)004:281: rgyu shes par shes pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:282: ting de goms nge 'dzin gsum gyi spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:283: spros pa'i gtsang ma spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:284: lnga pa bar chad med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:285: de nas rig 'dzin gyi spyod pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:287: bstan bya ba'i pa dang bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:288: de la dgu ste dgos bdag ched dang /
NK075(bu)004:291: bye brag tu sbyin sreg gi rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)004:293: dus skabs khyad par dang ces mi bskang skyon dang /
NK075(bu)004:296: don gyi spyi'i rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)004:297: bre brag lam gyi rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)004:299: lam spyi'i rnam grangs dang las ngo bo bzhi ngo bo'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)004:302: snga ma thabs dang shes rab kyis rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:303: de la mjug gsum du bsdu bya thabs la gnyis te //
NK075(bu)004:305: shes rab grol lam gyi bya thabs so //
NK075(bu)004:306: de la de la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:308: bye brag tu phye ba'i thabs so //
NK075(bu)004:310: phyi rol tshad med pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:314: bye brag tu sbyin sreg bya thabs so //
NK075(bu)004:317: bya thabs las kyi rim pa'oka //
NK075(bu)004:318: nga dgos bzhi po'i ched dang dus thun mong ba dang /
NK075(bu)004:330: skabs gang du dgos pa dang ca /
NK075(bu)004:331: kha dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:334: de la brgyad de gsang sgor ngo bo dang /
NK075(bu)004:338: bsrung bya che ba dang yon ma nor tan dang /
NK075(bu)004:342: bkod pa'i bstan pa dang bshad de de pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:346: rnam rtsa ba grangs dang ga /
NK075(bu)004:347: cha dus kyi yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)004:353: don 'gyur dgos lung dang rgyu rkyen dang /
NK075(bu)004:359: rgyu nyid snod dang skyon di zlog no //
NK075(bu)004:361: don tu bstan pa dang bshad pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:365: me long rnam grangs yon tan dang /
NK075(bu)004:370: sngags dang phyag rgya la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:379: dkyil 'khor skabs gang du dgos pa dang /
NK075(bu)004:381: gsang ba gang gi spyod yul yin pa'o //
NK075(bu)004:383: rig sngags sngags kyi rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)004:389: phyag rgya chen po'i zhes rnam grangs dang /
NK075(bu)004:390: dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i dang /
NK075(bu)004:391: las bsam dang kyi phyag rgya'i dang /
NK075(bu)004:392: chos bde ba kyi phyag rgya'i rnam grangs so //
NK075(bu)004:393: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:414: thams cad gdul bya'i gzigs tshul dang /
NK075(bu)004:415: bder gshegs thugs rjes sprul pa snang tshul dang /
NK075(bu)004:416: sgyu ma mdzad pa bya byed kyi rtsol ba med par don mdzad tshul dang /
NK075(bu)004:418: dus gsum dgongs pa'i rgyud kyi gnas tshul gcig dang
NK075(bu)004:419: du ma las grol ba smra bsam las 'das par
NK075(bu)004:420: bstan pa'o // thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK075(bu)004:421: bdag ces don du rang snang du thob pa'i tshul dang /
NK075(bu)004:422: gzhan ces don du mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs nas thob tshul lo //
